    <div class="aux section__modules">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="grid__item one-whole lap--one-half desk--one-half section__module">
                <img src="../image/scissors.jpeg" alt="Data encryption">
                <h4>Data encryption</h4>
                <p>All your financial information in Google Wallet is encrypted and stored on Google’s protected servers in secure locations. If needed, you can quickly remove access to your account on any device at <a href="https://security.google.com/settings/security/activity" target="_blank">myaccount.google.com.</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid__item one-whole lap--one-half desk--one-half section__module">
                <img src="../image/scissors.jpeg" alt="Fraud protection">
                <h4>Fraud protection</h4>
                <p>Google Wallet comes with 24/7 fraud monitoring and covers 100% of all verified unauthorized transactions.</p>
                <p class="cta-links">
                    <a href="https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/3026245" data-g-label="Google Wallet Fraud Protection" target="_blank">Google Wallet Fraud Protection</a>
                    <span class="divider">|</span>
                    <a href="https://support.google.com/wallet/contact/unrecognized_charge" data-g-label="File a Claim" target="_blank">File a Claim</a>
                </p>
            </div>
